Dan, thanks.

I=92m filled with joy this morning and wanted to share with you some wonder=
ful news. We had a major win at Ross Video today: TIM student Anni Bhasker =
presented her TIM project report to the Ross Video team =97 and she absolut=
ely knocked it out of the park! The Ross folks were delighted with her work=
 and are already asking for more.
This success is a powerful reminder of what our TIM students are capable of=
. When we bring interesting opportunities to them, set high expectations, s=
upport them to stretch, and challenge them to rise to the occasion, they tr=
uly can move mountains. Anni=92s achievement is just one example of the gre=
at things we can expect from our TIM students when standards, mentorship, a=
nd good opportunities come together.
I=92m very proud of our TIM students =97 and excited for the many more vict=
ories they will have ahead.
Warm regards,
Tony, a very happy TIM Academic Director



